*&quot;G-class&quot; G30, G40, G50, G60, G70 (&quot;Nova&quot; / &quot;Nova64&quot;)
*&quot;H-class&quot; H20, H30, H40, H50, H60, H70
*&quot;I-class&quot; I30, I40, I50, I60, I70
