=== Awards ===
In 2005 Cardinal was awarded The Distinguished Artist Award from the Lieutenant Governor of Alberta for &quot;creating an indigenous style of Canadian architecture, characterized by gracious organic forms, which continually challenged the most advanced engineering standards&quot;.

